input_str: In the OGN eStadium in Seoul (29th), the 2nd round of the 2017 LoL KeSPA Cup quarterfinals took place between Longzhu Gaming and Jin Air Greenwings. Longzhu Gaming went 2:1 against Jin Air and qualified for the semi finals. Considered one of the best players in the player market, Peanut transferred from SKT T1 to Longzhu and made his appearance on the main stage.
